---
// src/pages/privacy.astro
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
import { ShieldCheck } from 'lucide-react';

const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' });
---

<LandingLayout title="Privacy Policy - Ocha Healthcare" description="How we collect, use, and protect your data.">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-[#276CA1] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        <ShieldCheck className="w-4 h-4" />
        Legal
      </span>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none prose-headings:font-serif prose-a:text-[#276CA1]">
      
      <h3>1. Introduction</h3>
      <p>
        Welcome to Ocha Healthcare ("we," "our," or "us"). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. 
        This privacy policy explains how we look after your personal data when you visit our website (ocha.health) and tell you about your privacy rights.
      </p>

      <h3>2. Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>We may collect, use, store, and transfer different kinds of personal data about you which we have grouped together follows:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Identity Data:</strong> Name, username, or similar identifier provided via WhatsApp or forms.</li>
        <li><strong>Contact Data:</strong> Phone number and email address.</li>
        <li><strong>Health Data:</strong> Limited medical information you voluntarily share (e.g., "I need a heart specialist") to help us connect you with the right doctor.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use our website, tracked via Microsoft Clarity and Google Analytics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>3. How We Use Your Data</h3>
      <p>We strictly use your data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Connect you with medical providers (Hospitals/Doctors) at your request.</li>
        <li>Send you the guides or cost estimates you requested.</li>
        <li>Improve our website experience using heatmaps and usage metrics (Microsoft Clarity).</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>We never sell your data to third-party advertisers.</strong></p>

      <h3>4. Cookies and Tracking</h3>
      <p>
        We use cookies and similar tracking technologies (such as <strong>Microsoft Clarity</strong> and <strong>Google Analytics</strong>) to track the activity on our Service and store certain information. 
        These tools help us understand how users interact with our site (e.g., which pages are most popular) to improve our user experience.
      </p>

      <h3>5. Third-Party Links</h3>
      <p>
        Our website may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., Hospital official sites, WhatsApp). Clicking on those links may allow third parties to collect or share data about you. 
        We do not control these third-party websites and are not responsible for their privacy statements.
      </p>

      <h3>6. Contact Us</h3>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via WhatsApp or email.</p>

    </div>
  </main>
</LandingLayout>